  ('real-estate-appraiser-moex-00450', 'real-estate-appraiser', 'real-estate-appraiser-moex-098-ba81c82b', 'sub-real-estate-appraiser-04', NULL, 'essay', '目前臺灣地區各城市正在興建及規劃捷運系統，請以阿隆索（Alonso）之競價地租
